half of their own dollars

00:54:37.941 --> 00:54:41.611 align:middle line:84%
to get this movie made,
which is not an easy thing

00:54:41.611 --> 00:54:44.714 align:middle line:84%
to do in this inflationary
world with the mainstream hating

00:54:44.714 --> 00:54:45.548 align:middle line:90%
your topic.

00:54:45.548 --> 00:54:46.816 align:middle line:90%
And they finally got it done.

