And if so, hopefully
there's some listeners here

00:54:58.261 --> 00:54:59.629 align:middle line:84%
and in other parts
of the country

00:54:59.629 --> 00:55:00.997 align:middle line:90%
that will go and see it.

00:55:00.997 --> 00:55:03.199 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: It's finished, so I
