>>HOFFMAN: It's premiering
on the 22nd of March.

00:55:07.304 --> 00:55:08.905 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: You don't
get an advanced copy?

00:55:08.905 --> 00:55:09.973 align:middle line:90%
>>HOFFMAN: No.

00:55:09.973 --> 00:55:11.241 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: Oh, I'd be
very curious to see

00:55:11.241 --> 00:55:13.543 align:middle line:84%
what you think about it in
terms of its commentary.

00:55:13.543 --> 00:55:14.377 align:middle line:84%
>>HOFFMAN: Well, I
love the trailer.

00:55:14.377 --> 00:55:15.712 align:middle line:90%
Actually, I have the comic book.

00:55:15.712 --> 00:55:17.947 align:middle line:84%
I've seen a bit of
what it's about.

00:55:17.947 --> 00:55:19.649 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: So are we
along for a fun ride?

00:55:19.649 --> 00:55:21.151 align:middle line:84%
And do you think
that it's poignant?

00:55:21.151 --> 00:55:22.285 align:middle line:90%
>>HOFFMAN: Absolutely.

00:55:22.285 --> 00:55:24.621 align:middle line:84%
I think it's as relevant
as anything out there.

00:55:24.621 --> 00:55:27.324 align:middle line:84%
And more importantly,
it's done by youth.

00:55:27.324 --> 00:55:31.561 align:middle line:84%
It's young people that
believe in a good cause

00:55:31.561 --> 00:55:34.197 align:middle line:84%
and have put blood, sweat,
and tears into this film.

00:55:34.197 --> 00:55:35.699 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: Speaking
of which, we only

00:55:35.699 --> 00:55:38.635 align:middle line:90%
have a couple minutes left.

