the under 30s?

00:55:45.008 --> 00:55:48.445 align:middle line:84%
People in their 20s graduating
from college, student debt.

00:55:48.445 --> 00:55:49.579 align:middle line:90%
>>HOFFMAN: The Millennials.

00:55:49.579 --> 00:55:50.814 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: The Millennials.

00:55:50.814 --> 00:55:52.949 align:middle line:84%
>>HOFFMAN: Or as a guy I
read named Gerald Celente--

00:55:52.949 --> 00:55:54.050 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: Yes, I like him.

00:55:54.050 --> 00:55:56.252 align:middle line:84%
>>HOFFMAN: He calls
