00:55:56.252 --> 00:55:58.955 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: Yeah, F'd.

00:55:58.955 --> 00:56:00.757 align:middle line:84%
>>HOFFMAN: I mean, not
to make light of it,

00:56:00.757 --> 00:56:04.294 align:middle line:84%
but it's an extremely
difficult situation.

