I do podcasts all the time.

00:56:05.762 --> 00:56:07.330 align:middle line:84%
I probably do three
or four a week.

00:56:07.330 --> 00:56:10.066 align:middle line:84%
And I'm starting to do a
bunch with young people.

00:56:10.066 --> 00:56:11.234 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: Oh, good.

00:56:11.234 --> 00:56:12.936 align:middle line:84%
>>HOFFMAN: One is 16
years old, a bunch of them

00:56:12.936 --> 00:56:15.038 align:middle line:84%
are college kids,
very smart that

00:56:15.038 --> 00:56:16.706 align:middle line:84%
are really into
the topics today.

00:56:16.706 --> 00:56:17.707 align:middle line:90%
And they're worried.

00:56:17.707 --> 00:56:18.808 align:middle line:90%
They're fearful.

00:56:18.808 --> 00:56:20.543 align:middle line:84%
They live with their
parents, most of them.

00:56:20.543 --> 00:56:22.746 align:middle line:84%
They are not sure what
the future is going to be.

00:56:26.216 --> 00:56:27.951 align:middle line:84%
The only advice I could
give is the advice

00:56:27.951 --> 00:56:30.754 align:middle line:84%
I would have given to myself
back then, is to just work hard

00:56:30.754 --> 00:56:32.022 align:middle line:90%
and be focused.

00:56:32.022 --> 00:56:34.591 align:middle line:84%
And just, you have
to have optimism

00:56:34.591 --> 00:56:36.826 align:middle line:84%
because there's a lot
of good in the world.

00:56:36.826 --> 00:56:37.327 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: Absolutely.

00:56:37.327 --> 00:56:38.495 align:middle line:90%
There is.

00:56:38.495 --> 00:56:40.196 align:middle line:84%
I mean, the world is
still, on so many levels,

00:56:40.196 --> 00:56:40.997 align:middle line:90%
a beautiful place.

00:56:40.997 --> 00:56:42.198 align:middle line:90%
We all still have each other.

00:56:42.198 --> 00:56:44.200 align:middle line:84%
We all still--
ideally, if we can

00:56:44.200 --> 00:56:47.337 align:middle line:84%
take a little responsibility,
have good food available to us

00:56:47.337 --> 00:56:47.837 align:middle line:90%
even.

